      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison metrics (e.g., NRMSE, validation uncertainty) must be reported for the hemolysis index and at least one secondary QoI.",
      "rationale": "NRMSE for the hemolysis index is 18% across validation points; validation uncertainty intervals overlap experimental uncertainty at 3 of 5 points. Secondary QoI (wall shear stress) comparison is qualitative only. Achieved level is below required."
